						<!-- About me content - left aligned, taking up more space -->
						<div class="md:col-span-3 space-y-6">
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
								My name is Marcos. I'm a Cuban-born statistics student and aspiring financial advisor with a growing obsession in answering the question "What lessons does history hide?"
							</p>
							<p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
